Travelers Real Estate Investment Trust    Qtly div 17 cts vs 23 cts in prior qtr    Payable November 25    Record October 30    It said the lower dividend reflects the reduction in cashflow from a mortgage secured by a motel in Covington, La.    The trust said an appraisal is being made of the Covingtonproperty to determine whether an increase in loss reserve willbe required at year end.       Travelers REIT said its investment adviser, Keystone RealtyAdvisers has committed to lend the trust up to 500,000 dlrs fora term of two years to cover past due payables and capitalimprovements on the Covington motel.    Keystone Realty is an affiliate of the Keystone Group, aTraverlers Corp &lt;TIC> subsidiary. Reuter&#3;